# Token Optimization Configuration

## DOM Distillation Rules

```json
{{
  "rules": [
    {
      "name": "strip_non_interactive",
      "description": "Remove non-interactive elements",
      "selectors": [
        "script, style, link[href*='.css'], noscript",
        "meta, head, [hidden]",
        "div:not([onclick]):not([onchange]):not([onsubmit])",
        "span:not([onclick])"
      ]
    }},
    {
      "name": "compact_attributes",
      "description": "Keep only essential attributes",
      "keep_attributes": [
        "id", "class", "aria-label", "aria-role", "role",
        "name", "type", "placeholder", "value"
      ],
      "remove_attributes": [
        "data-*", "style", "onclick", "onchange", "data-*"
      ]
    }},
    {
      "name": "text_content_optimization",
      "description": "Optimize text representation",
      "rules": [
        "Truncate text to 100 chars",
        "Remove leading/trailing whitespace",
        "Normalize whitespace"
      ]
    }}
  ]
}}
```

## Element Representation

```json
{{
  "format": "compact",
  "template": "[{id}] {tag}: {text}",
  "max_elements": 100,
  "priority": "clickables > inputs > text"
}}
```

## Page Content Optimization

```json
{{
  "sections": [
    {{
      "name": "main_content",
      "selector": "main, article, .content",
      "max_elements": 30
    }},
    {{
      "name": "navigation",
      "selector": "nav, .nav, .navigation",
      "max_elements": 20
    }},
    {{
      "name": "forms",
      "selector": "form, .form",
      "max_elements": 15
    }}
  ]
}}
```

## Context Compression

```json
{{
  "strategy": "selective_inclusion",
  "rules": [
    {
      "condition": "simple_navigation",
      "include": ["buttons", "links", "inputs"],
      "exclude": ["scripts", "styles", "iframes"]
    }},
    {
      "condition": "complex_task",
      "include": ["all_interactive", "semantic_structure"],
      "exclude": ["hidden", "invisible"]
    }}
  ]
}}
```

## Template Caching

```json
{{
  "cache_strategy": "preload_common",
  "templates": [
    "simple_navigation",
    "form_filling",
    "dropdown_selection",
    "button_click",
    "link_follow"
  ],
  "cache_ttl_seconds": 3600
}}
```

## Performance Metrics

```json
{{
  "metrics": {
    "tokens_per_action": "target: 800, max: 1500",
    "response_time_ms": "target: 2000, max: 5000",
    "success_rate": "target: 0.95, min: 0.90",
    "token_reduction": "target: 0.50, min: 0.40"
  },
  "tracking": {
    "enabled": true,
    "sample_rate": 1.0,
    "log_all_actions": true
  }
}}
```

## API Endpoints

- **GET** `/api/v1/prompts/optimization/config` - Get optimization config
- **PUT** `/api/v1/prompts/optimization/config` - Update optimization config
- **GET** `/api/v1/prompts/optimization/metrics` - Get optimization metrics
- **POST** `/api/v1/prompts/optimization/test` - Test optimization strategy

## MCP Tools

- `get_optimization_config` - Get current optimization configuration
- `update_optimization_config` - Update optimization settings
- `reset_optimization_metrics` - Reset performance metrics
